      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows some noticeable scuffs and minor paint fading in areas, while the interior displays typical wear and tear from regular use. Mechanically, it remains reliable and has been serviced to ensure it stays road-ready. It is a solid choice for those prioritizing utility and value over a flawless appearance.",
