      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute stunner. It's in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this beauty since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
